One or more event cases have no events defined

An event case is not configured to handle an event.

To correct this error, complete the following steps.

  1. Make sure the case you want to edit is visible.
  2. Right-click the Event structure.
  3. Select Edit Events Handled by This Case from the shortcut menu to display the Edit Events dialog box.
  4. Edit the case to handle a specific event.

Before you configure events for the Event structure to handle, review the caveats and recommendations for using events in LabVIEW.
